flowchart TD
    A[cartId受領] --> B[HQLでCartProduct一覧取得]
    B --> C{明細有?}
    C -- No --> D[空List返却]
    C -- Yes --> E[for each CartProduct]
    E --> F{product != null ?}
    F -- Yes --> G[products に追加]
    F -- No --> H[skip]
    G --> I{次明細有?}
    H --> I
    I -- Yes --> E
    I -- No --> J[Product一覧返却]